/interviews/common-ace2-variants-no-effect-physiology" class="ajax-exclude">Common ACE2 variants: no effect on physiology</a></h4></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="panel-separator"></div><div class="panel-pane pane-custom-pagers-pane" ><div class="pane-content"><ul class="custom-pager custom-pager-bottom"><li class="previous"> <span class="custom-pager-title">Previous</span> <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-chevron-left" aria-hidden="true"></span> <a href="/podcasts/elife-podcast/psychedelic-drugs-and-river-water-bugs">Psychedelic drugs and river water bugs</a></li><li class="next"> <span class="custom-pager-title">Next</span> <a href="/podcasts/naked-scientists-podcast/secret-life-seeds">The Secret Life of Seeds</a> <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-chevron-right" aria-hidden="true"></span></li></ul></div></div></div><div class="panel-pane pane-views-panes pane-subscribe-feed-panel-pane-2 subscribe-links-node" ><h2 class="pane-title"> Subscribe for free</h2><div class="pane-content"><div class="view view-subscribe-feed view-id-subscribe_feed view-display-id-panel_pane_2 view-dom-id-23622e5958ab4c14f16e51b0ae674350"><div class="view-content"><div class="views-row views-row-1 views-row-odd views-row-first views-row-last"><div class="views-field views-field-nothing"> <span class="field-content"><div class="subscribe-podcast"><a href="/node/197414" class="btn btn-md btn-green-ghost"><i class="fa fa-rss" aria-hidden="true"></i><span class="hidden-xs"> Subscribe to Naked Genetics</span></a></div></span></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="panel-separator"></div><div class="panel-pane pane-node-comment-wrapper" ><div class="pane-content"><div id="comments" class="comment-wrapper comment-wrapper-nid-199447"><h2 class="title">Comments</h2><div class="ajax-comment-wrapper ajax-comment-dummy-comment" style="display:none"><div class="form-item form-type-item form-group"></div></div><h2 class="title comment-form">Add a comment</h2><form class="comment-fo